subject: RE: Changes ARE in DEVL — try git fetch + reset
body:
Hey Quinn,

The changes ARE in origin/DEVL:

```
ba000d2a fix: Change admin routes to admin/ops/* to avoid Azure conflict
```

Routes in remote:
- Admin_DataHealth: route: 'admin/ops/data-health'
- Admin_UserActivity: route: 'admin/ops/user-activity'

## Try This

Your local branch might be detached or diverged. Try:

```bash
cd ~/MyDocs/AppDev/MasterCalendar/calendar-be-af
git fetch origin
git checkout DEVL
git reset --hard origin/DEVL
```

Then verify:
```bash
grep 'route:' src/functions/Admin_DataHealth.js
# Should show: route: 'admin/ops/data-health'
```

Then restart func.

— Fulton
